init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The film begins, and you see yourself as a baby, being born.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see your mother and father, and the doctor.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see the room you were born in, and the first time you were held.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a toddler, and your first day of school.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a teenager, and your first kiss.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a young adult, and your first car.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a middle-aged man, and your first child.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as an old man, and your last breath.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are dead, and you are in Heaven.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She is dressed in a long white robe, and her hair is long and flowing.
